<view class="rule-page data-v-01f0653d"><view class="rule-title data-v-01f0653d">📋 排队系统使用说明</view><view class="rule-section data-v-01f0653d"><view class="section-title data-v-01f0653d">1️⃣ 如何排队</view><view class="section-content data-v-01f0653d"> • 点击首页"我要排队"按钮<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 填写车牌号、司机姓名、联系电话<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 选择车辆类型（5.2米/6.8米/9.6米/13米/17.5米）<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 选择装车或卸车<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 选择预计到达时间<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 如果是卸车，需填写卸货地址<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 点击"提交"完成排队 </view></view><view class="rule-section data-v-01f0653d"><view class="section-title data-v-01f0653d">2️⃣ 排队状态</view><view class="section-content data-v-01f0653d"><view class="status-item data-v-01f0653d"><text class="status-badge processing data-v-01f0653d">处理中</text><text class="data-v-01f0653d">您的车辆正在装卸货，请按指引操作</text></view><view class="status-item data-v-01f0653d"><text class="status-badge waiting data-v-01f0653d">排队中</text><text class="data-v-01f0653d">请耐心等待，首页可查看当前排号</text></view></view></view><view class="rule-section data-v-01f0653d"><view class="section-title data-v-01f0653d">3️⃣ 修改信息</view><view class="section-content data-v-01f0653d"> • 排队后如需修改信息，点击首页"修改信息"<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 修改后重新提交即可<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 修改不影响您的排队顺序 </view></view><view class="rule-section data-v-01f0653d"><view class="section-title data-v-01f0653d">4️⃣ 完成流程</view><view class="section-content data-v-01f0653d"> • 当您的车辆完成装卸货后<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 点击首页"卸车完成"按钮<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 上传现场照片作为凭证<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 提交后自动通知下一位司机 </view></view><view class="rule-section data-v-01f0653d"><view class="section-title data-v-01f0653d">5️⃣ 消息通知</view><view class="section-content data-v-01f0653d"> • 排队成功后会收到微信服务通知<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 快轮到您时会提前提醒<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 轮到您时会立即通知<view class="data-v-01f0653d"/> • 请保持微信消息通知开启 </view></view><view class="rule-tips data-v-01f0653d"><view 